  <brief_title>Clinical and Laboratory Characteristics of Sickle Cell Anemia Patients Admitted With Fever</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study the Clinical and Laboratory Characteristics and the Outcome of Sickle Cell Anemia Patients Admitted to the Pediatric Ward Because of Fever as the Presenting Symptom</official_title>
