  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will summarized the clinical and laboratory data and the outcome of all the
      patients suffering from Sickle Cell Anemia (Including Sickle cell thalassemia) admitted to
      the pediatric ward.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The actual protocol for SCA patients admitted with fever is to obtain blood cultures and
      start empiric antibiotic treatment.

      The study cohort included 60 SCA patients actually treated in the Pediatric Hematology Unit.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
